Q1) Create a HTTPD server and host a website.
->
Create a EC2 
Connect from powershell
  SSH -i ./file path for .pem-open file Username@PublicIP
Install HTTPD
  yum install httpd
start the server
  Sudo systemctl start httpd
Check status
  Sudo Systemctl Status httpd
Start by default
  Sudo Systemctl enable --now httpd
get the HTML file save it on the location var/www/html/
copy the public IP and paste on the browser
